1953) bụ nwanyị ọchụnta ego Naijiria bụ onye isi oche nke Access Bank plc. Tupu nhọpụta a, ọ bụ odeakwụkwọ na-adịgide adịgide na Federal Ministries of Internal Affairs, Sayensị & Teknụzụ na Ike n'oge dị iche iche

E boro ya ebubo na ọ na-azụ ahịa ime ihe. A mụrụ Awosika na Sapele, nwa nke isii nke onye minista na-ahụ maka ego na Naijiria na mba mbụ Festus Okotie-Eboh, onye e gburu na 1966. Ọ bụ onye otu Pharmaceutical Society of Nigeria na West African Postgraduate College of Pharmacy
Ọ bụ onye gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Bradford, ebe o nwere doctorate
